107. Telegram From the Department of State to the Embassy in FranceSource: National Archives, RG 59, Central Files 1970–73, CUL 8.
                        Unclassified. Drafted by Hurd;
                        cleared by telephone by Teal,
                            Nelson, and E. Skora (ABRC);
                        approved by Blair. Hurd initialed for the clearing officials
                        and for Blair.
